data.comment: The match is underway in Enschede.
Nick Bakker is booked for the away team.
The first-half has come to a close in Enschede.
In the minute 45, Vaclav Cerny (Enschede) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 46, The away team replace Hilal Ben Moussa with Michael Chacon.
The away team have replaced Marko Kolar with Anco Jansen. This is the first substitution made today by Dick Lukkien.
Vaclav Cerny scores to make it 1-0 at Grolsch Veste Stadium.
In the minute 48, Great play from Ramiz Zerrouki to set up the goal.
Ron Jans (Enschede) is making a first substitution, with Lindon Selahi replacing Jesse Bosch.
Michael de Leeuw grabs a goal to bring things level at 1-1 at Grolsch Veste Stadium.
In the minute 74, Enschede make their second substitution with Lazaros Lamprou replacing Queensy Menig.
Godfried Roemeratoe is on a sub for Ramiz Zerrouki for Enschede.
Leeuwen Thijs Van is replacing Danilo for the home team.
In the minute 87, Ron Jans is making the team's fourth substitution at Grolsch Veste Stadium with Dario Dumic replacing Kik Pierie.
The match has come to a close in Enschede. The final score is 1-1.
